      "content": "therapists dont really get it tho. they just try to give me tools to \"cope\" with it, but coping is just more work. it's like being told to learn how to breathe underwater when you're clearly drowning. i feel like im just waiting for something to break. im just so tired of the noise and the effort of existing. everything feels so heavy and pointless all the time.",
